What I'm going to do is come up with a program that randomly generates

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:09.000
decks or deals from the deck and then checks to see

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:13.000
what kind it is and checks to see if we can reproduce this probability table.

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:17.000
We're going to look at random deal percentages,

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:19.000
and first we're going to have a quiz.

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:22.000
Say we want to deal out a random number of hands

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.000
and then count how many of each type we have

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:27.000
and then come up with that table like we just saw from Wikipedia.

